title: From the Back Street to Main Street...And Beyond: History of the Society of Methodists of Middletown Point
description: From the Back Street to Main Street...and Beyond chronicles the Society of Methodists of Middletown Point from the organization's early beginnings with circuit rider preachers through to the 21st century as the Matawan United Methodist Church at Aberdeen. Author Helen Henderson blends the context of times past with 100 images as she presents over 180 years of the church's history and that of the Monmouth County (New Jersey) towns that became Aberdeen Township and Matawan Borough. (from back cover)
author: Helen B. Henderson
